#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_dcshift.xml:4
#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_dcshift.xml:10
#, kde-format
msgid "DC shift"
msgstr "DC shift"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_dcshift.xml:7
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Apply a DC shift to the audio.\n"
"This can be useful to remove a DC offset (caused perhaps by a hardware "
"problem in the recording chain) from the audio.\n"
"The effect of a DC offset is reduced headroom and hence volume. The astats "
"filter can be used to determine if a signal has a DC offset."
msgstr ""
"ໃຊ້ DC shift ກັບສຽງ.\n"
"ສິ່ງນີ້ສາມາດເປັນປະໂຫຍດໃນການລຶບ DC offset (ອາດເກີດຈາກບັນຫາຮາດແວໃນຕ່ອງໂສ້ການບັນທຶກ) "
"ອອກຈາກສຽງ.\n"
"ຜົນຂອງ DC offset ແມ່ນ headroom ຫຼຸດລົງ ແລະ ດັ່ງນັ້ນລະດັບສຽງກໍຫຼຸດລົງ. ຟິວເຕີ astats "
"ສາມາດໃຊ້ເພື່ອກຳນົດວ່າສັນຍານມີ DC offset ຫຼືບໍ່."

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_dcshift.xml:11
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Set the DC shift, allowed range is [-1, 1]. It indicates the amount to shift "
"the audio."
msgstr "ຕັ້ງຄ່າ DC shift, ຊ່ວງທີ່ອະນຸຍາດແມ່ນ [-1, 1]. ມັນບົ່ງບອກປະລິມານທີ່ຈະ shift ສຽງ."

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_dcshift.xml:14
#, kde-format
msgid "Limiter gain"
msgstr "ອັດຕາຂະຫຍາຍ Limiter"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_dcshift.xml:15
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Optional. It should have a value much less than 1 (e.g. 0.05 or 0.02) and is "
"used to prevent clipping."
msgstr ""
"ທາງເລືອກ. ມັນຄວນຈະມີຄ່ານ້ອຍກວ່າ 1 ຫຼາຍ (ເຊັ່ນ: 0.05 ຫຼື 0.02) ແລະ ຖືກໃຊ້ເພື່ອປ້ອງກັນ clipping."

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_dctdnoiz.xml:4
#, kde-format
msgid "DCT Denoiser"
msgstr "DCT Denoiser"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_dctdnoiz.xml:5
#, kde-format
msgid "Denoise frames using 2D DCT frequency domain filtering"
