#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_deband.xml:5
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Remove banding artifacts from input video. It works by replacing banded "
"pixels with average value of referenced pixels"
msgstr ""
"ລຶບ banding artifacts ອອກຈາກວິດີໂອຂາເຂົ້າ. ມັນເຮັດວຽກໂດຍການແທນທີ່ພິກເຊວທີ່ເປັນ banding "
"ດ້ວຍຄ່າສະເລ່ຍຂອງພິກເຊວອ້າງອີງ"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_deband.xml:8
#, kde-format
msgid "1st plane threshold"
msgstr "ເກນແຜ່ນທີ 1"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_deband.xml:10
#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_deband.xml:15
#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_deband.xml:20
#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_deband.xml:25
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Sets banding detection threshold for each plane.<br>\n"
"        If difference between current pixel and reference pixel is less than "
"threshold, it will be considered as banded."
msgstr ""
"ຕັ້ງຄ່າເກນການກວດຈັບ banding ສຳລັບແຕ່ລະແຜ່ນ.<br>\n"
"        ຖ້າຄວາມແຕກຕ່າງລະຫວ່າງພິກເຊວປັດຈຸບັນ ແລະ ພິກເຊວອ້າງອີງນ້ອຍກວ່າເກນ, "
"ມັນຈະຖືກພິຈາລະນາວ່າເປັນ banding."

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_deband.xml:13
#, kde-format
msgid "2nd plane threshold"
msgstr "ເກນແຜ່ນທີ 2"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_deband.xml:18
#, kde-format
msgid "3rd plane threshold"
msgstr "ເກນແຜ່ນທີ 3"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_deband.xml:23
#, kde-format
msgid "4th plane threshold"
msgstr "ເກນແຜ່ນທີ 4"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_deband.xml:30
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Banding detection range in pixels. Default is 16.<br>\n"
"        If positive, random number in range 0 to set value will be used. If "
"negative, exact absolute value will be used. The range defines square of "
"four pixels around current pixel."
msgstr ""
"ຊ່ວງການກວດຈັບ Banding ເປັນພິກເຊວ. ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແມ່ນ 16.<br>\n"
"        ຖ້າເປັນຄ່າບວກ, ຕົວເລກສຸ່ມໃນຊ່ວງ 0 ຫາຄ່າທີ່ຕັ້ງໄວ້ຈະຖືກໃຊ້. ຖ້າເປັນຄ່າລົບ, ຄ່າ absolute "
"ທີ່ແນ່ນອນຈະຖືກໃຊ້. ຊ່ວງກຳນົດສີ່ຫຼ່ຽມຂອງສີ່ພິກເຊວອ້ອມຮອບພິກເຊວປັດຈຸບັນ."

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_deband.xml:33
#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_transpose.xml:8
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_aech0r.xml:12 data/effects/timer.xml:103
#: data/transitions/slide.xml:8
#, kde-format
msgid "Direction"
msgstr "ທິດທາງ"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_deband.xml:35
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Sets direction in degrees from which four pixel will be compared.<br>\n"
"        If positive, random direction from 0 to set direction will be "
"picked. If negative, exact of absolute value will be picked. For example "
"direction 0°, -180°, or -360° will pick only pixels on same row and -90° "
"will pick only pixels on same column"
msgstr ""
"ຕັ້ງທິດທາງເປັນອົງສາຈາກບ່ອນທີ່ສີ່ພິກເຊວຈະຖືກປຽບທຽບ.<br>\n"
"        ຖ້າເປັນຄ່າບວກ, ທິດທາງສຸ່ມຈາກ 0 ຫາທິດທາງທີ່ຕັ້ງໄວ້ຈະຖືກເລືອກ. ຖ້າເປັນຄ່າລົບ, ຄ່າ "
"absolute ທີ່ແນ່ນອນຈະຖືກເລືອກ. ຕົວຢ່າງ ທິດທາງ 0°, -180°, ຫຼື -360° "
"ຈະເລືອກພຽງແຕ່ພິກເຊວໃນແຖວດຽວກັນ ແລະ -90° ຈະເລືອກພຽງແຕ່ພິກເຊວໃນຖັນດຽວກັນ"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_deband.xml:38
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bgsubtract0r.xml:14
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_glow.xml:8
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_mask0mate.xml:18 data/effects/pillar_echo.xml:11
#: data/effects/tracker.xml:31
#, kde-format
msgid "Blur"
msgstr "ເບີ"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_deband.xml:40
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"If enabled, current pixel is compared with average value of all four "
"surrounding pixels.<br>\n"
"        The default is enabled. If disabled, current pixel is compared with "
"all four surrounding pixels. The pixel is considered banded if only all four "
"differences with surrounding pixels are less than threshold."
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າເປີດໃຊ້ງານ, ພິກເຊວປັດຈຸບັນຈະຖືກປຽບທຽບກັບຄ່າສະເລ່ຍຂອງສີ່ພິກເຊວອ້ອມຂ້າງທັງໝົດ.<br>\n"
"        ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແມ່ນເປີດໃຊ້ງານ. ຖ້າປິດໃຊ້ງານ, "
"ພິກເຊວປັດຈຸບັນຈະຖືກປຽບທຽບກັບສີ່ພິກເຊວອ້ອມຂ້າງທັງໝົດ. ພິກເຊວຈະຖືກພິຈາລະນາວ່າເປັນ banded "
"ຖ້າຄວາມແຕກຕ່າງກັບພິກເຊວອ້ອມຂ້າງທັງສີ່ນ້ອຍກວ່າເກນເທົ່ານັ້ນ."

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_deband.xml:43
#, kde-format
msgid "Coupling"
msgstr "Coupling"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_deband.xml:45
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"If enabled, current pixel is changed if and only if<br>\n"
"        all pixel components are banded, e.g. banding detection threshold is "
"triggered for all color components. The default is disabled."
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າເປີດໃຊ້ງານ, ພິກເຊວປັດຈຸບັນຈະຖືກປ່ຽນຖ້າແລະພຽງແຕ່ຖ້າ<br>\n"
"        ອົງປະກອບພິກເຊວທັງໝົດເປັນ banded, ເຊັ່ນ: ເກນການກວດຈັບ banding "
"ຖືກກະຕຸ້ນສຳລັບອົງປະກອບສີທັງໝົດ. ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແມ່ນປິດໃຊ້ງານ."

