msgstr "ແປງລຳດັບຟີວຂອງວິດີໂອຂາເຂົ້າ."

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_fillborders.xml:4
#, kde-format
msgid "Fill Borders"
msgstr "ຕື່ມຂອບ"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_fillborders.xml:5
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Fill borders of the input video without changing video stream dimensions. "
"Sometimes video can have garbage at the four edges and you may not want to "
"crop video input to keep the size multiple of some number"
msgstr ""
"ຕື່ມຂອບຂອງວິດີໂອຂາເຂົ້າໂດຍບໍ່ປ່ຽນຂະໜາດຂອງວິດີໂອ. ບາງຄັ້ງວິດີໂອອາດມີສ່ວນເກີນຢູ່ທີ່ຂອບທັງສີ່ ແລະ "
"ເຈົ້າອາດບໍ່ຕ້ອງການຕັດວິດີໂອອອກເພື່ອຮັກສາຂະໜາດໃຫ້ເປັນພະຫຸຄູນຂອງຕົວເລກໃດໜຶ່ງ"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_fillborders.xml:9
#, kde-format
msgid "Smear,Mirror,Color,Reflect,Wrap,Fade,Margins"
msgstr "ທາສີ (Smear),ແວ່ນ (Mirror),ສີ,ສະທ້ອນ,ຫໍ່ຫຸ້ມ,ຈາງລົງ,ຂອບ"

