#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_gradfun.xml:4
#, fuzzy, kde-format
#| msgid "gradfun"
msgid "Gradfun"
msgstr "gradfun"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_gradfun.xml:8
#, fuzzy, kde-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<b>-= Deprecated =-</b><br>\n"
#| "    Debands video quickly using gradients.<br>\n"
#| "    Fix the banding artifacts that are sometimes introduced into nearly "
#| "flat regions by truncation to 8-bit color depth.<br>\n"
#| "    Interpolate the gradients that should go where the bands are, and "
#| "dither them.<br>\n"
#| "    <b>It is designed for playback only. Do not use it prior to lossy "
#| "compression, because compression tends to lose the dither and bring back "
#| "the bands</b>."
msgid ""
"Debands video quickly using gradients.<br>\n"
"    Fix the banding artifacts that are sometimes introduced into nearly flat "
"regions by truncation to 8-bit color depth.<br>\n"
"    Interpolate the gradients that should go where the bands are, and dither "
"them.<br><br>\n"
"    <b><i>It is designed for playback only. Do not use it prior to lossy "
"compression, because compression tends to lose the dither and bring back the "
"bands</i></b>."
msgstr ""
"<b>-= ເລີກໃຊ້ແລ້ວ =-</b><br>\n"
"    ລຸດຮອຍແຖບສີ (Deband) ໃນວິດີໂອຢ່າງໄວວາໂດຍໃຊ້ການໄລ່ສີ.<br>\n"
"    ແກ້ໄຂຮອຍແຖບສີທີ່ບາງຄັ້ງເກີດຂຶ້ນໃນພື້ນທີ່ລຽບ ຍ້ອນການຕັດທອນເປັນຄວາມເລິກສີ 8-bit.<br>\n"
"    ຄຳນວນຄ່າແຊກການໄລ່ສີໃນບ່ອນທີ່ມີແຖບສີ ແລະ dither ພວກມັນ.<br>\n"
"    <b>ມັນຖືກອອກແບບມາສຳລັບການຫຼິ້ນເທົ່ານັ້ນ. ຢ່າໃຊ້ມັນກ່ອນການບີບອັດແບບ lossy, "
"ເພາະການບີບອັດມັກຈະເຮັດໃຫ້ dither ຫາຍໄປ ແລະ ເຮັດໃຫ້ແຖບສີກັບມາອີກ</b>."

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_gradfun.xml:13
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The maximum amount by which the filter will change any one pixel.<br>\n"
"       \tThis is also the threshold for detecting nearly flat regions."
msgstr ""
"ຈຳນວນສູງສຸດທີ່ຟິວເຕີຈະປ່ຽນແປງພິກເຊວໃດໜຶ່ງ.<br>\n"
"       \tອັນນີ້ຍັງເປັນເກນ (threshold) ສຳລັບການກວດຈັບພື້ນທີ່ທີ່ເກືອບຈະລຽບ."

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_gradfun.xml:18
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The neighborhood to fit the gradient to.<br>\n"
"       \tA larger radius makes for smoother gradients, but also prevents the "
"filter from modifying the pixels near detailed regions."
msgstr ""
"ບໍລິເວນໃກ້ຄຽງທີ່ຈະປັບການໄລ່ສີໃສ່.<br>\n"
"       \tລັດສະໝີທີ່ໃຫຍ່ກວ່າຈະເຮັດໃຫ້ການໄລ່ສີລຽບນຽນກວ່າ, "
"ແຕ່ຍັງປ້ອງກັນບໍ່ໃຫ້ຟິວເຕີແກ້ໄຂພິກເຊວໃກ້ກັບພື້ນທີ່ທີ່ມີລາຍລະອຽດ."

