#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_smartblur.xml:5
#, kde-format
msgid "Blur the input video without impacting the outlines. "
msgstr "ເຮັດໃຫ້ວິດີໂອຂາເຂົ້າທີ່ມົວ ໂດຍບໍ່ກະທົບຕໍ່ເສັ້ນຂອບ. "

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_smartblur.xml:8
#, kde-format
msgid "Luma radius"
msgstr "ລັດສະໝີ Luma"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_smartblur.xml:10
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Set the luma radius.<br>\n"
"            The value specifies the variance of the gaussian filter used to "
"blur the image (slower if larger)."
msgstr ""
"ຕັ້ງຄ່າລັດສະໝີ luma.<br>\n"
"            ຄ່ານີ້ລະບຸຄວາມປ່ຽນແປງຂອງ gaussian filter ທີ່ໃຊ້ເພື່ອເຮັດໃຫ້ຮູບພາບມົວ "
"(ຊ້າລົງຖ້າໃຫຍ່ກວ່າ)."

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_smartblur.xml:13
#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_unsharp.xml:17
#, kde-format
msgid "Luma strength"
msgstr "ຄວາມແຮງ Luma"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_smartblur.xml:15
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Set the luma strength.<br>\n"
"            The value configures the blurring. A positive value will blur "
"the image, whereas a negative value will sharpen the image."
msgstr ""
"ຕັ້ງຄ່າຄວາມແຮງ luma.<br>\n"
"            ຄ່ານີ້ກຳນົດການເຮັດໃຫ້ມົວ. ຄ່າບວກຈະເຮັດໃຫ້ຮູບພາບມົວ, "
"ໃນຂະນະທີ່ຄ່າລົບຈະເຮັດໃຫ້ຮູບພາບຄົມຊັດຂຶ້ນ."

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_smartblur.xml:18
#, kde-format
msgid "Luma threshold"
msgstr "Luma threshold"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_smartblur.xml:20
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Set the luma threshold used as a coefficient<br>\n"
"            to determine whether a pixel should be blurred or not. A value "
"of 0 will filter all the image, positive values will filter flat areas, "
"negative values will filter edges."
msgstr ""
"ຕັ້ງຄ່າ luma threshold ທີ່ໃຊ້ເປັນສຳປະສິດ<br>\n"
"            ເພື່ອກຳນົດວ່າພິກເຊວຄວນຈະຖືກເຮັດໃຫ້ມົວຫຼືບໍ່. ຄ່າ 0 ຈະກັ່ນຕອງທັງໝົດຮູບພາບ, "
"ຄ່າບວກຈະກັ່ນຕອງພື້ນທີ່ຮາບພຽງ, ຄ່າລົບຈະກັ່ນຕອງຂອບ."

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_smartblur.xml:23
#, kde-format
msgid "Chroma radius"
msgstr "ລັດສະໝີ Chroma"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_smartblur.xml:25
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Set the chroma radius.<br>\n"
"            The value specifies the variance of the gaussian filter used to "
"blur the image (slower if larger). If not specified, it defaults to the "
"value set for <em>Luma radius</em>"
msgstr ""
"ຕັ້ງຄ່າລັດສະໝີ chroma.<br>\n"
"            ຄ່ານີ້ລະບຸຄວາມປ່ຽນແປງຂອງ gaussian filter ທີ່ໃຊ້ເພື່ອເຮັດໃຫ້ຮູບພາບມົວ "
"(ຊ້າລົງຖ້າໃຫຍ່ກວ່າ). ຖ້າບໍ່ລະບຸ, ມັນຈະໃຊ້ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຕາມທີ່ຕັ້ງໄວ້ສຳລັບ <em>Luma radius</em>"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_smartblur.xml:28
#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_unsharp.xml:30
#, kde-format
msgid "Chroma strength"
msgstr "ຄວາມແຮງ Chroma"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_smartblur.xml:30
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Set the chroma strength.<br>\n"
"            The value configures the blurring. A positive value will blur "
"the image, whereas a negative value will sharpen the image. If not "
"specified, it defaults to the value set for <em>Luma strength</em>."
msgstr ""
"ຕັ້ງຄ່າຄວາມແຮງ chroma.<br>\n"
"            ຄ່ານີ້ກຳນົດການເຮັດໃຫ້ມົວ. ຄ່າບວກຈະເຮັດໃຫ້ຮູບພາບມົວ, "
"ໃນຂະນະທີ່ຄ່າລົບຈະເຮັດໃຫ້ຮູບພາບຄົມຊັດຂຶ້ນ. ຖ້າບໍ່ລະບຸ, ມັນຈະໃຊ້ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຕາມທີ່ຕັ້ງໄວ້ສຳລັບ <em>Luma "
"strength</em>."

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_smartblur.xml:33
#, kde-format
msgid "Chroma threshold"
msgstr "Chroma threshold"

#: data/effects/avfilter/avfilter_smartblur.xml:35
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Set the chroma threshold used as a coefficient<br>\n"
"            to determine whether a pixel should be blurred or not. A value "
