#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_mask.xml:4
#, kde-format
msgid "VR360 Equirectangular Mask"
msgstr "VR360 Equirectangular Mask"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_mask.xml:5
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Adds a black matte to the frame. Use this if you filmed using a 360 camera "
"but only want to use part of the 360 image - for example if you and the film "
"crew occupy the 90 degrees behind the camera."
msgstr ""
"ເພີ່ມພື້ນສີດຳ (Matte) ໃສ່ເຟຣມ. ໃຊ້ອັນນີ້ຖ້າເຈົ້າຖ່າຍດ້ວຍກ້ອງ 360 ແຕ່ຕ້ອງການໃຊ້ພຽງສ່ວນໜຶ່ງຂອງຮູບ 360 "
"- ຕົວຢ່າງເຊັ່ນ ຖ້າເຈົ້າ ແລະ ທີມງານຖ່າຍທຳ ຢູ່ໃນມຸມ 90 ອົງສາດ້ານຫຼັງກ້ອງ."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_mask.xml:8
#, kde-format
msgid "Vertical start"
msgstr "ຈຸດເລີ່ມຕົ້ນທາງຕັ້ງ"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_mask.xml:9
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid ""
"The <b>Start</b> is half the height in degrees of the un-matted area. The "
"<b>End</b> is the half the height in degrees where the matte is at 100%."
msgstr ""
"<b>ຈຸດເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ</b> ແມ່ນເຄິ່ງໜຶ່ງຂອງຄວາມສູງໃນໜ່ວຍອົງສາ ຂອງພື້ນທີ່ທີ່ບໍ່ຖືກບັງ. <b>ຈຸດສິ້ນສຸດ</b> "
"ແມ່ນເຄິ່ງໜຶ່ງຂອງຄວາມສູງໃນໜ່ວຍອົງສາ ບ່ອນທີ່ການບັງຢູ່ທີ່ 100%."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_mask.xml:12
#, kde-format
msgid "Vertical end"
msgstr "ຈຸດສິ້ນສຸດທາງຕັ້ງ"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_mask.xml:13
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid ""
"The Start is half the height in degrees of the un-matted area. The End is "
"the half the height in degrees where the matte is at 100%."
msgstr ""
"ຈຸດເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ ແມ່ນເຄິ່ງໜຶ່ງຂອງຄວາມສູງໃນໜ່ວຍອົງສາ ຂອງພື້ນທີ່ທີ່ບໍ່ຖືກບັງ. ຈຸດສິ້ນສຸດ "
"ແມ່ນເຄິ່ງໜຶ່ງຂອງຄວາມສູງໃນໜ່ວຍອົງສາ ບ່ອນທີ່ການບັງຢູ່ທີ່ 100%."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_mask.xml:16
#, kde-format
msgid "Horizontal start"
msgstr "ຈຸດເລີ່ມຕົ້ນທາງນອນ"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_mask.xml:17
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_mask.xml:21
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid ""
"The <b>Start</b> is the width in degrees of the un-matted area. The <b>End</"
"b> is the width in degrees where the matte is at 100%."
msgstr ""
"<b>ຈຸດເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ</b> ແມ່ນຄວາມກວ້າງໃນໜ່ວຍອົງສາ ຂອງພື້ນທີ່ທີ່ບໍ່ຖືກບັງ. <b>ຈຸດສິ້ນສຸດ</b> "
"ແມ່ນຄວາມກວ້າງໃນໜ່ວຍອົງສາ ບ່ອນທີ່ການບັງຢູ່ທີ່ 100%."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_mask.xml:20
#, kde-format
msgid "Horizontal end"
msgstr "ຈຸດສິ້ນສຸດທາງນອນ"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_to_rect.xml:4
#, kde-format
msgid "VR360 Equirectangular to Rectilinear"
msgstr "VR360 Equirectangular ເປັນ Rectilinear"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_to_rect.xml:5
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Converts an equirectangular frame (panoramic) to a rectilinear frame (what "
"you're used to seeing). Can be used to preview what will be shown in a 360 "
"video viewer. Delayed frame blitting mapped on a time bitmap"
msgstr ""
"ແປງເຟຣມ Equirectangular (ພາໂນຣາມາ) ໃຫ້ເປັນເຟຣມ Rectilinear (ແບບປົກກະຕິ). "
"ສາມາດໃຊ້ເພື່ອເບິ່ງຕົວຢ່າງສິ່ງທີ່ຈະສະແດງໃນໂປຣແກຣມເບິ່ງວິດີໂອ 360. Delayed frame blitting "
"mapped on a time bitmap"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_to_rect.xml:8
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_to_stereo.xml:8
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_transform_360.xml:8
#, kde-format
msgid "Yaw"
msgstr "ຫັນຊ້າຍຂວາ (Yaw)"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_to_rect.xml:10
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_transform_360.xml:10
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The amount to rotate the image<br>\n"
"    \t(nose moves from side to side)."
msgstr ""
"ຈຳນວນທີ່ຈະໝຸນຮູບ<br>\n"
"    \t(ຫັນຈາກຂ້າງໜຶ່ງໄປອີກຂ້າງໜຶ່ງ)."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_to_rect.xml:13
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_to_stereo.xml:11
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_transform_360.xml:13
#, kde-format
msgid "Pitch"
msgstr "ກົ້ມເງີຍ (Pitch)"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_to_rect.xml:15
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_transform_360.xml:15
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The amount to rotate the image<br>\n"
"    \t(nose up or down)."
msgstr ""
"ຈຳນວນທີ່ຈະໝຸນຮູບ<br>\n"
"    \t(ກົ້ມລົງ ຫຼື ເງີຍຂຶ້ນ)."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_to_rect.xml:18
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_to_stereo.xml:14
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_transform_360.xml:18
#, kde-format
msgid "Roll"
msgstr "ມຸນອຽງ (Roll)"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_to_rect.xml:20
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_transform_360.xml:20
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The amount to rotate the image<br>\n"
"    \t(clockwise or anticlockwise rotation along the axis of movement)."
msgstr ""
"ຈຳນວນທີ່ຈະໝຸນຮູບ<br>\n"
"    \t(ໝຸນຕາມເຂັມ ຫຼື ທວນເຂັມໂມງ ຕາມແກນການເຄື່ອນໄຫວ)."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_to_rect.xml:23
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_to_stereo.xml:17
#, kde-format
msgid "FOV"
msgstr "ມຸມມອງ (FOV)"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_to_rect.xml:25
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The horizontal field of view, in degrees, of the resulting frame.<br>\n"
"    \tAny value over 179 results in a fisheye projection."
msgstr ""
"ມຸມມອງທາງນອນ (ເປັນອົງສາ) ຂອງເຟຣມຜົນຮັບ.<br>\n"
"    \tຄ່າທີ່ເກີນ 179 ຈະສົ່ງຜົນໃຫ້ເປັນພາບແບບຕາປາ (fisheye projection)."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_to_rect.xml:28
#, kde-format
msgid "Fisheye"
msgstr "ຕາປາ (Fisheye)"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_to_rect.xml:30
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid ""
"The amount of fisheye to mix in.<br>\n"
"    \t100 means that you get a 100% fisheye lens."
msgstr ""
"ຈຳນວນຂອງເອັບເຟັກຕາປາທີ່ຈະປະສົມເຂົ້າໄປ.<br>\n"
"    \t100 ໝາຍຄວາມວ່າເຈົ້າຈະໄດ້ເລນຕາປາແບບ 100%."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_to_stereo.xml:4
#, kde-format
msgid "VR360 Equirectangular to Stereo"
msgstr "VR360 Equirectangular ເປັນ Stereo"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_to_stereo.xml:5
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Projects a stereographic image from an equirectangular. Use this to create "
"the little planet effect from a VR360 footage."
msgstr ""
"ສາຍພາບ stereographic ຈາກ equirectangular. ໃຊ້ອັນນີ້ເພື່ອສ້າງເອັບເຟັກ Little Planet "
"ຈາກຟຸດເທດ VR360."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_to_stereo.xml:24
#, kde-format
msgid "Nearest-neighbor,Bilinear"
msgstr "Nearest-neighbor,Bilinear"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_wrap.xml:4
#, kde-format
msgid "VR360 Wrap"
msgstr "VR360 Wrap"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_wrap.xml:5
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Stretches a section of the equirectangular panorama to cover the entire VR "
"sphere"
msgstr "ຢືດສ່ວນຂອງພາໂນຣາມາແບບ equirectangular ໃຫ້ປົກຄຸມທົ່ວໜ່ວຍໂລກ VR"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_wrap.xml:9
#, kde-format
msgid "Determines the sampling method"
msgstr "ກຳນົດວິທີການເກັບຕົວຢ່າງ"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_wrap.xml:14
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_wrap.xml:18
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_wrap.xml:22
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_wrap.xml:26
#, kde-format
msgid "Degrees from the center of the image to keep unchanged"
msgstr "ອົງສາຈາກຈຸດສູນກາງຂອງຮູບທີ່ຈະຮັກສາໄວ້ບໍ່ໃຫ້ປ່ຽນແປງ"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_wrap.xml:29
#, kde-format
msgid "Blur start"
msgstr "ເລີ່ມມົວ"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_wrap.xml:30
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Horizontal fraction of the unchanged area to blur over in the equator band"
msgstr "ສັດສ່ວນທາງນອນຂອງພື້ນທີ່ທີ່ບໍ່ປ່ຽນແປງ ທີ່ຈະເຮັດໃຫ້ມົວໃນແຖບເສັ້ນສູນສູດ"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_wrap.xml:33
#, kde-format
msgid "Blur end"
msgstr "ສິ້ນສຸດຄວາມມົວ"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_eq_wrap.xml:34
#, kde-format
msgid "Horizontal fraction of the unchanged area to blur over at the poles"
msgstr "ສັດສ່ວນທາງນອນຂອງພື້ນທີ່ທີ່ບໍ່ປ່ຽນແປງ ທີ່ຈະເຮັດໃຫ້ມົວຢູ່ຂົ້ວ"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:4
#, kde-format
msgid "VR360 Hemispherical to Equirectangular"
msgstr "VR360 Hemispherical ເປັນ Equirectangular"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:5
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Converts a video frame with two hemispherical images to a single "
"equirectangular frame. The plugin assumes that both hemispheres are in the "
"frame"
msgstr ""
"ແປງເຟຣມວິດີໂອທີ່ມີສອງຮູບເຄິ່ງວົງກົມ ໃຫ້ເປັນເຟຣມ equirectangular ດຽວ. "
"ປັລກອິນສົມມຸດວ່າທັງສອງເຄິ່ງວົງກົມຢູ່ໃນເຟຣມແລ້ວ"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:8
#, kde-format
msgid "Alignment yaw"
msgstr "ການຈັດລຽງ Yaw"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:10
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:15
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:20
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The two fisheye cameras of a 360 camera are rarely perfectly 180 degrees "
"apart.<br>\n"
"    \tThese parameters adds a rotation to both lenses to correct for this."
msgstr ""
"ກ້ອງຕາປາສອງຕົວຂອງກ້ອງ 360 ບໍ່ຄ່ອຍຈະຢູ່ຫ່າງກັນ 180 ອົງສາພໍດີ.<br>\n"
"    \tພາລາມິເຕີເຫຼົ່ານີ້ຈະເພີ່ມການໝຸນໃຫ້ທັງສອງເລນເພື່ອແກ້ໄຂບັນຫານີ້."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:13
#, kde-format
msgid "Alignment pitch"
msgstr "ການຈັດລຽງ Pitch"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:18
#, kde-format
msgid "Alignment roll"
msgstr "ການຈັດລຽງ Roll"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:23
#, kde-format
msgid "Projection"
msgstr "ການສາຍພາບ (Projection)"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:24
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The fisheye projection type. Currently only equidistant fisheyes, like the "
"Ricoh Theta and Garmin Virb360 are supported."
msgstr ""
"ປະເພດຂອງ fisheye projection. ປັດຈຸບັນຮອງຮັບສະເພາະ equidistant fisheyes, ເຊັ່ນ "
"Ricoh Theta ແລະ Garmin Virb360."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:25
#, kde-format
msgid "Equidistant Fisheye"
msgstr "Equidistant Fisheye"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:28
#, kde-format
msgid "Lens FOV"
msgstr "ມຸມມອງເລນ (FOV)"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:29
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The field of view of a single hemisphere in degrees, expressed as a fraction "
"of the frame width."
msgstr "ມຸມມອງຂອງເຄິ່ງວົງກົມດຽວໃນໜ່ວຍອົງສາ, ສະແດງເປັນເສດສ່ວນຂອງຄວາມກວ້າງເຟຣມ."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:32
#, kde-format
msgid "Lens radius"
msgstr "ລັດສະໝີເລນ"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:33
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The radius of the image circle, expressed as a fraction of the frame width."
msgstr "ລັດສະໝີຂອງວົງກົມຮູບພາບ, ສະແດງເປັນເສດສ່ວນຂອງຄວາມກວ້າງເຟຣມ."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:36
#, kde-format
msgid "Front X"
msgstr "ດ້ານໜ້າ X"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:38
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The image center and image orientation for the front-facing camera.<br>\n"
"    \tThe X parameter is a fraction of the image width."
msgstr ""
"ຈຸດສູນກາງຮູບພາບ ແລະ ທິດທາງຂອງຮູບພາບສຳລັບກ້ອງດ້ານໜ້າ.<br>\n"
"    \tພາລາມິເຕີ X ແມ່ນເສດສ່ວນຂອງຄວາມກວ້າງຮູບພາບ."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:41
#, kde-format
msgid "Front Y"
msgstr "ດ້ານໜ້າ Y"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:43
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The image center and image orientation for the front-facing camera.<br>\n"
"    \tThe Y parameter a fraction of the image height."
msgstr ""
"ຈຸດສູນກາງຮູບພາບ ແລະ ທິດທາງຂອງຮູບພາບສຳລັບກ້ອງດ້ານໜ້າ.<br>\n"
"    \tພາລາມິເຕີ Y ແມ່ນເສດສ່ວນຂອງຄວາມສູງຮູບພາບ."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:46
#, kde-format
msgid "Front Up"
msgstr "ດ້ານໜ້າ Up"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:48
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The image center and image orientation for the front-facing camera.<br>\n"
"    \tUp is the \"up\" direction in the image, in degrees clockwise from a "
"direction towards the frame top edge."
msgstr ""
"ຈຸດສູນກາງຮູບພາບ ແລະ ທິດທາງຂອງຮູບພາບສຳລັບກ້ອງດ້ານໜ້າ.<br>\n"
"    \tUp ແມ່ນທິດທາງ \"ຂຶ້ນ\" ໃນຮູບພາບ, ເປັນອົງສາຕາມເຂັມໂມງ ຈາກທິດທາງໄປຫາຂອບເທິງຂອງເຟຣມ."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:51
#, kde-format
msgid "Back X"
msgstr "ດ້ານຫຼັງ X"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:53
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The image center and image orientation for the back-facing camera.<br>\n"
"    \tThe X parameter is a fraction of the image width.."
msgstr ""
"ຈຸດສູນກາງຮູບພາບ ແລະ ທິດທາງຂອງຮູບພາບສຳລັບກ້ອງດ້ານຫຼັງ.<br>\n"
"    \tພາລາມິເຕີ X ແມ່ນເສດສ່ວນຂອງຄວາມກວ້າງຮູບພາບ."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:56
#, kde-format
msgid "Back Y"
msgstr "ດ້ານຫຼັງ Y"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:58
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The image center and image orientation for the back-facing camera.<br>\n"
"    \tThe Y parameter a fraction of the image height."
msgstr ""
"ຈຸດສູນກາງຮູບພາບ ແລະ ທິດທາງຂອງຮູບພາບສຳລັບກ້ອງດ້ານຫຼັງ.<br>\n"
"    \tພາລາມິເຕີ Y ແມ່ນເສດສ່ວນຂອງຄວາມສູງຮູບພາບ."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:61
#, kde-format
msgid "Back Up"
msgstr "ດ້ານຫຼັງ Up"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:63
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The image center and image orientation for the back-facing camera.<br>\n"
"    \tUp is the \"up\" direction in the image, in degrees clockwise from a "
"direction towards the frame top edge."
msgstr ""
"ຈຸດສູນກາງຮູບພາບ ແລະ ທິດທາງຂອງຮູບພາບສຳລັບກ້ອງດ້ານຫຼັງ.<br>\n"
"    \tUp ແມ່ນທິດທາງ \"ຂຶ້ນ\" ໃນຮູບພາບ, ເປັນອົງສາຕາມເຂັມໂມງ ຈາກທິດທາງໄປຫາຂອບເທິງຂອງເຟຣມ."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:66
#, kde-format
msgid "Nadir radius"
msgstr "ລັດສະໝີ Nadir (ກົ້ນ)"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:68
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:73
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"360 cameras like the Theta have a problem with the nadir direction where, no "
"matter what, you will have a little of the camera in the image.<br>\n"
"    \tThis parameter \"stretches\" the image near nadir to cover up the "
"missing parts."
msgstr ""
"ກ້ອງ 360 ເຊັ່ນ Theta ມີບັນຫາກັບທິດທາງ Nadir ບ່ອນທີ່ເຈົ້າຈະເຫັນຕົວຕົ້ນຂອງກ້ອງໃນຮູບພາບເລັກນ້ອຍສະເໝີ."
"<br>\n"
"    \tພາລາມິເຕີນີ້ຈະ \"ຢືດ\" ຮູບພາບໃກ້ກັບ Nadir ເພື່ອປົກປິດສ່ວນທີ່ຂາດຫາຍໄປ."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:71
#, kde-format
msgid "Nadir start"
msgstr "ຈຸດເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ Nadir"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:76
#, kde-format
msgid "Lens distortion A"
msgstr "ການບິດເບືອນເລນ A"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:78
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:83
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:88
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Lens distortion correction parameters.<br>\n"
"    \tThe first three parameters are the same as in Hugin."
msgstr ""
"ພາລາມິເຕີແກ້ໄຂການບິດເບືອນຂອງເລນ.<br>\n"
"    \tສາມພາລາມິເຕີທຳອິດແມ່ນຄືກັນກັບໃນ Hugin."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:81
#, kde-format
msgid "Lens distortion B"
msgstr "ການບິດເບືອນເລນ B"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:86
#, kde-format
msgid "Lens distortion C"
msgstr "ການບິດເບືອນເລນ C"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:91
#, kde-format
msgid "Lens distortion radius"
msgstr "ລັດສະໝີການບິດເບືອນເລນ"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:93
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Lens distortion correction parameters.<br>\n"
"    \tIf you use Hugin parameters, the Radius should be set to the value of "
"(0.5 * min(image width, image height) / image width). For a 2:1 aspect dual "
"hemispherical image, that would be 0.25."
msgstr ""
"ພາລາມິເຕີແກ້ໄຂການບິດເບືອນຂອງເລນ.<br>\n"
"    \tຖ້າເຈົ້າໃຊ້ພາລາມິເຕີ Hugin, ລັດສະໝີຄວນຕັ້ງເປັນຄ່າຂອງ (0.5 * min(image width, image "
"height) / image width). ສຳລັບຮູບພາບ dual hemispherical ອັດຕາສ່ວນ 2:1, ຄ່ານັ້ນຈະແມ່ນ "
"0.25."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:96
#, kde-format
msgid "Lens vignetting A"
msgstr "Lens vignetting A"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:98
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:103
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:108
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:113
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Lens vignetting correction parameters.<br>\n"
"    \tThe first four parameters are the same as in Hugin, corresponding to "
"the Va, Vb, Vc and Vd image parameters."
msgstr ""
"ພາລາມິເຕີແກ້ໄຂ Lens vignetting.<br>\n"
"    \tສີ່ພາລາມິເຕີທຳອິດແມ່ນຄືກັນກັບໃນ Hugin, ກົງກັບພາລາມິເຕີຮູບພາບ Va, Vb, Vc ແລະ Vd."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:101
#, kde-format
msgid "Lens vignetting B"
msgstr "Lens vignetting B"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:106
#, kde-format
msgid "Lens vignetting C"
msgstr "Lens vignetting C"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:111
#, kde-format
msgid "Lens vignetting D"
msgstr "Lens vignetting D"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:116
#, kde-format
msgid "Lens vignetting radius"
msgstr "ລັດສະໝີ Lens vignetting"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:118
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"If you use Hugin parameters, the radius should be set to the value of (0.5 * "
"image diagonal / image width).<br>\n"
"    \tFor a 2:1 aspect dual hemispherical image, that would be 0.5590. Use "
"the A parameter to scale the effect and avoid overexposing highlights"
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າເຈົ້າໃຊ້ພາລາມິເຕີ Hugin, ລັດສະໝີຄວນຕັ້ງເປັນຄ່າຂອງ (0.5 * image diagonal / image "
"width).<br>\n"
"    \tສຳລັບຮູບພາບ dual hemispherical ອັດຕາສ່ວນ 2:1, ຄ່ານັ້ນຈະແມ່ນ 0.5590. ໃຊ້ພາລາມິເຕີ "
"A ເພື່ອປັບຂະໜາດເອັບເຟັກ ແລະ ຫຼີກເວັ້ນການແຈ້ງເກີນໄປຂອງໄຮໄລ"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:121
#, kde-format
msgid "Use sensor response parameters"
msgstr "ໃຊ້ພາລາມິເຕີການຕອບສະໜອງຂອງເຊັນເຊີ"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:122
#, kde-format
msgid "Switch on to use sensor response parameters (EMoR h(x))"
msgstr "ເປີດໃຊ້ເພື່ອໃຊ້ພາລາມິເຕີການຕອບສະໜອງຂອງເຊັນເຊີ (EMoR h(x))"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:125
#, kde-format
msgid "EMoR h(1)"
msgstr "EMoR h(1)"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:127
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:132
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:137
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:142
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:147
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Sensor response parameters.<br>\n"
"    \tThe EMoR h(x) parameters are the same as Hugin's Ra - Re in the lens "
"parameters. If you use Hugin-derived values for vignetting correction, you "
"should also use these parameters, as Hugin's vignetting correction assumes "
"that the sensor response has been corrected."
msgstr ""
"ພາລາມິເຕີການຕອບສະໜອງຂອງເຊັນເຊີ.<br>\n"
"    \tພາລາມິເຕີ EMoR h(x) ແມ່ນຄືກັນກັບ Ra - Re ຂອງ Hugin ໃນພາລາມິເຕີເລນ. "
"ຖ້າເຈົ້າໃຊ້ຄ່າທີ່ໄດ້ຈາກ Hugin ສຳລັບການແກ້ໄຂ vignetting, ເຈົ້າຄວນໃຊ້ພາລາມິເຕີເຫຼົ່ານີ້ເຊັ່ນກັນ, "
"ເນື່ອງຈາກການແກ້ໄຂ vignetting ຂອງ Hugin ສົມມຸດວ່າການຕອບສະໜອງຂອງເຊັນເຊີໄດ້ຖືກແກ້ໄຂແລ້ວ."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:130
#, kde-format
msgid "EMoR h(2)"
msgstr "EMoR h(2)"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:135
#, kde-format
msgid "EMoR h(3)"
msgstr "EMoR h(3)"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:140
#, kde-format
msgid "EMoR h(4)"
msgstr "EMoR h(4)"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_hemi_to_eq.xml:145
#, kde-format
msgid "EMoR h(5)"
msgstr "EMoR h(5)"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_rect_to_eq.xml:4
#, kde-format
msgid "VR360 Rectilinear to Equirectangular"
msgstr "VR360 Rectilinear ເປັນ Equirectangular"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_rect_to_eq.xml:5
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Converts a rectilinear (a normal-looking) image to an equirectangular image. "
"Use this together with Transform 360 to place \"normal\" footage in a 360 "
"movie."
msgstr ""
"ແປງຮູບ rectilinear (ຮູບປົກກະຕິ) ໃຫ້ເປັນຮູບ equirectangular. ໃຊ້ອັນນີ້ຮ່ວມກັບ Transform "
"360 ເພື່ອວາງຟຸດເທດ \"ປົກກະຕິ\" ລົງໃນໜັງ 360."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:4
#, kde-format
msgid "VR360 Stabilize"
msgstr "VR360 ເຮັດໃຫ້ພາບນິ້ງ"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:6
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Stabilizes 360 footage.<br>\n"
"    The plugin works in two phases - analysis and stabilization. When "
"analyzing footage, it detects frame-to-frame rotation, and when stabilizing "
"it tries to correct high-frequency motion (shake)."
msgstr ""
"ເຮັດໃຫ້ຟຸດເທດ 360 ນິ້ງ.<br>\n"
"    ປັລກອິນເຮັດວຽກໃນສອງໄລຍະ - ການວິເຄາະ ແລະ ການເຮັດໃຫ້ນິ້ງ. ເມື່ອວິເຄາະຟຸດເທດ, "
"ມັນຈະກວດຈັບການໝຸນລະຫວ່າງເຟຣມ, ແລະ ເມື່ອເຮັດໃຫ້ນິ້ງ ມັນຈະພະຍາຍາມແກ້ໄຂການເຄື່ອນໄຫວຄວາມຖີ່ສູງ "
"(ການສັ່ນ)."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:9
#, kde-format
msgid "Analyze"
msgstr "ວິເຄາະ"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:10
#, kde-format
msgid "Switch on for analysis phase; switch off for stabilization phase."
msgstr "ເປີດສຳລັບໄລຍະການວິເຄາະ; ປິດສຳລັບໄລຍະການເຮັດໃຫ້ນິ້ງ."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:13
#, kde-format
msgid "Motion analysis file"
msgstr "ໄຟລ໌ວິເຄາະການເຄື່ອນໄຫວ"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:14
#, kde-format
msgid "Select the file to store stabilization data in"
msgstr "ເລືອກໄຟລ໌ເພື່ອເກັບຂໍ້ມູນການເຮັດໃຫ້ນິ້ງ"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:17
#, kde-format
msgid "Start offset"
msgstr "Offset ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:19
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The offset into the stabilization file that corresponds to the start of this "
"clip.<br>\n"
"    \tFor example, if you have a 30 second clip, analyze it all, and then "
"split it into three clips of 10 seconds each, then the start offsets should "
"be 0s, 10s, and 20s."
msgstr ""
"Offset ເຂົ້າໃນໄຟລ໌ການເຮັດໃຫ້ນິ້ງ ທີ່ກົງກັບຈຸດເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຂອງຄລິບນີ້.<br>\n"
"    \tຕົວຢ່າງ, ຖ້າເຈົ້າມີຄລິບ 30 ວິນາທີ, ວິເຄາະທັງໝົດ, ແລ້ວແຍກເປັນສາມຄລິບ 10 ວິນາທີ, ດັ່ງນັ້ນ "
"offset ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຄວນຈະເປັນ 0s, 10s, ແລະ 20s."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:22
#, kde-format
msgid "Analysis sample radius"
msgstr "ລັດສະໝີຕົວຢ່າງການວິເຄາະ"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:23
#, kde-format
msgid "The radius of the square that the stabilizer will sample"
msgstr "ລັດສະໝີຂອງສີ່ຫຼ່ຽມທີ່ຕົວເຮັດໃຫ້ນິ້ງຈະເກັບຕົວຢ່າງ"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:26
#, kde-format
msgid "Analysis search radius"
msgstr "ລັດສະໝີການຄົ້ນຫາການວິເຄາະ"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:27
#, kde-format
msgid "The maximum amount of motion the stabilizer will detect"
msgstr "ຈຳນວນການເຄື່ອນໄຫວສູງສຸດທີ່ຕົວເຮັດໃຫ້ນິ້ງຈະກວດຈັບ"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:30
#, kde-format
msgid "Analysis offset"
msgstr "Offset ການວິເຄາະ"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:31
#, kde-format
msgid "The distance between the track points"
msgstr "ໄລຍະຫ່າງລະຫວ່າງຈຸດຕິດຕາມ"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:34
#, kde-format
msgid "Use backwards-facing track points"
msgstr "ໃຊ້ຈຸດຕິດຕາມທີ່ຫັນໄປທາງຫຼັງ"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:36
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"If set, six backwards-facing track points will also be used to detect pitch "
"and yaw motion.<br>\n"
"    \tDisable if, for example, you show up holding the camera there"
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າຕັ້ງຄ່າ, ຈຸດຕິດຕາມທີ່ຫັນໄປທາງຫຼັງ 6 ຈຸດ ຈະຖືກໃຊ້ເພື່ອກວດຈັບການເຄື່ອນໄຫວ pitch ແລະ yaw.<br>\n"
"    \tປິດການໃຊ້ງານຖ້າ, ຕົວຢ່າງເຊັ່ນ, ເຈົ້າປາກົດຕົວຖືກ້ອງຢູ່ບ່ອນນັ້ນ"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:39
#, kde-format
msgid "Yaw amount"
msgstr "ຈຳນວນ Yaw"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:41
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:69
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid ""
"The amount of stabilization to apply.<br>\n"
"    \t100% means that the stabilizer will make the camera as steady as it "
"can. Smaller values reduce the amount of stabilization."
msgstr ""
"ຈຳນວນການເຮັດໃຫ້ນິ້ງທີ່ຈະໃຊ້.<br>\n"
"    \t100% ໝາຍຄວາມວ່າຕົວເຮັດໃຫ້ນິ້ງຈະເຮັດໃຫ້ກ້ອງນິ້ງທີ່ສຸດເທົ່າທີ່ຈະເຮັດໄດ້. "
"ຄ່າທີ່ນ້ອຍກວ່າຈະຫຼຸດປະລິມານການເຮັດໃຫ້ນິ້ງ."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:44
#, kde-format
msgid "Yaw smoothing"
msgstr "ຄວາມລຽບນຽນຂອງ Yaw"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:45
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The number of frames to use to smooth out the shakes. The higher the value, "
"the slower the camera will follow any intended motion."
msgstr ""
"ຈຳນວນເຟຣມທີ່ຈະໃຊ້ເພື່ອເຮັດໃຫ້ການສັ່ນລຽບນຽນ. ຄ່າແຮງສູງ, ກ້ອງຈະຕິດຕາມການເຄື່ອນໄຫວທີ່ຕັ້ງໃຈໄດ້ຊ້າລົງ."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:48
#, kde-format
msgid "Yaw time bias"
msgstr "Yaw time bias"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:50
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:64
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:79
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Shift the frames used to smooth out the shakes relative to the stabilized "
"frame.<br>\n"
"    \tA value less than zero will give more weight to past frames, and the "
"camera will seem to lag behind intended movement. A value greater than zero "
"will give more weight to future frames, and the camera will appear to move "
"ahead of the intended camera movement. A value of zero should make the "
"camera follow the intended path."
msgstr ""
"ເລື່ອນເຟຣມທີ່ໃຊ້ເພື່ອເຮັດໃຫ້ການສັ່ນລຽບນຽນ ທຽບກັບເຟຣມທີ່ເຮັດໃຫ້ນິ້ງແລ້ວ.<br>\n"
"    \tຄ່າທີ່ນ້ອຍກວ່າສູນຈະໃຫ້ຄວາມສຳຄັນກັບເຟຣມໃນອະດີດຫຼາຍກວ່າ, ແລະ "
"ກ້ອງຈະເບິ່ງຄືວ່າມີການຊັກຊ້າກວ່າການເຄື່ອນໄຫວທີ່ຕັ້ງໃຈ. "
"ຄ່າທີ່ຫຼາຍກວ່າສູນຈະໃຫ້ຄວາມສຳຄັນກັບເຟຣມໃນອະນາຄົດຫຼາຍກວ່າ, ແລະ "
"ກ້ອງຈະເບິ່ງຄືວ່າເຄື່ອນທີ່ລ່ວງໜ້າການເຄື່ອນໄຫວທີ່ຕັ້ງໃຈ. ຄ່າສູນຄວນເຮັດໃຫ້ກ້ອງຕິດຕາມເສັ້ນທາງທີ່ຕັ້ງໃຈ."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:53
#, kde-format
msgid "Pitch amount"
msgstr "ຈຳນວນ Pitch"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:54
#, no-c-format, kde-format
msgid ""
"The amount of stabilization to apply. 100% means that the stabilizer will "
"make the camera as steady as it can. Smaller values reduce the amount of "
"stabilization."
msgstr ""
"ຈຳນວນການເຮັດໃຫ້ນິ້ງທີ່ຈະໃຊ້. 100% ໝາຍຄວາມວ່າຕົວເຮັດໃຫ້ນິ້ງຈະເຮັດໃຫ້ກ້ອງນິ້ງທີ່ສຸດເທົ່າທີ່ຈະເຮັດໄດ້. "
"ຄ່າທີ່ນ້ອຍກວ່າຈະຫຼຸດປະລິມານການເຮັດໃຫ້ນິ້ງ."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:57
#, kde-format
msgid "Pitch smoothing"
msgstr "ຄວາມລຽບນຽນຂອງ Pitch"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:59
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:74
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The number of frames to use to smooth out the shakes.<br>\n"
"    \tThe higher the value, the slower the camera will follow any intended "
"motion."
msgstr ""
"ຈຳນວນເຟຣມທີ່ຈະໃຊ້ເພື່ອເຮັດໃຫ້ການສັ່ນລຽບນຽນ.<br>\n"
"    \tຄ່າແຮງສູງ, ກ້ອງຈະຕິດຕາມການເຄື່ອນໄຫວທີ່ຕັ້ງໃຈໄດ້ຊ້າລົງ."

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:62
#, kde-format
msgid "Pitch time bias"
msgstr "Pitch time bias"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:67
#, kde-format
msgid "Roll amount"
msgstr "ຈຳນວນ Roll"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:72
#, kde-format
msgid "Roll smoothing"
msgstr "ຄວາມລຽບນຽນຂອງ Roll"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_stabilize_360.xml:77
#, kde-format
msgid "Roll time bias"
msgstr "Roll time bias"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_transform_360.xml:4
#, kde-format
msgid "VR360 Transform"
msgstr "VR360 Transform"

#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_bigsh0t_transform_360.xml:5
#, kde-format
