"Perform an RGB[A] divide operation between the pixel sources: input1 is the "
"numerator, input2 the denominator."
msgstr ""
"ປະຕິບັດການ RGB[A] divide ລະຫວ່າງແຫຼ່ງພິກເຊວ: input1 ແມ່ນຕົວຕັ້ງຫານ, input2 ແມ່ນຕົວຫານ."

#: data/transitions/frei0r/frei0r_dodge.xml:4
#, kde-format
msgid "Dodge"
msgstr "Dodge"

#: data/transitions/frei0r/frei0r_dodge.xml:5
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Perform an RGB[A] dodge operation between the pixel sources, using the "
"generalised algorithm: D = saturation of 255 or (A * 256) / (256 - B)"
msgstr ""
"ປະຕິບັດການ RGB[A] dodge ລະຫວ່າງແຫຼ່ງພິກເຊວ, ໂດຍໃຊ້ອັລກໍຣິທຶມທົ່ວໄປ: D = saturation ຂອງ "
"255 ຫຼື (A * 256) / (256 - B)"

#: data/transitions/frei0r/frei0r_euclid_eraser.xml:4
#, kde-format
msgid "Euclid Eraser"
msgstr "Euclid Eraser"

#: data/transitions/frei0r/frei0r_euclid_eraser.xml:5
#, kde-format
