msgstr "ລຶບພື້ນຫຼັງໂດຍໃຊ້ໄລຍະຫ່າງ euclidean."

#: data/transitions/frei0r/frei0r_euclid_eraser.xml:8
#, kde-format
msgid "Distance Threshold"
msgstr "Distance Threshold"

