#: src/dialogs/clipjobmanager.cpp:44
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"<b>{source}</b> will be replaced by the Bin Clip source file path, "
"<b>{param1}</b> will be replaced by the first parameter value, <b>{param2}</"
"b> will be replaced by the second parameter value, <b>{output}</b> will be "
"replaced by the output file name."
msgstr ""
"<b>{source}</b> ຈະຖືກແທນທີ່ດ້ວຍເສັ້ນທາງໄຟລ໌ຕົ້ນທາງຂອງຄລິບໃນຖັງ, <b>{param1}</b> "
"ຈະຖືກແທນທີ່ດ້ວຍຄ່າພາຣາມິເຕີທຳອິດ, <b>{param2}</b> ຈະຖືກແທນທີ່ດ້ວຍຄ່າພາຣາມິເຕີທີສອງ, "
"<b>{output}</b> ຈະຖືກແທນທີ່ດ້ວຍຊື່ໄຟລ໌ຜົນອອກ."

#: src/dialogs/clipjobmanager.cpp:46
#, kde-format
