#: src/titler/unicodedialog.cpp:181
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>An en Dash (dash of the width of an n).</p><p>Usage examples: In English "
"language for value ranges (1878&#x2013;1903), for relationships/connections "
"(Zurich&#x2013;Dublin). In the German language it is also used (with "
"spaces!) for showing thoughts: &ldquo;Es war &#x2013; wie immer in den "
"Ferien &#x2013; ein regnerischer Tag.</p> <p>See <a href=\"https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/Dash\">Wikipedia:Dash</a></p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>En Dash (ຂີດທີ່ມີຄວາມກວ້າງຂອງ n).</p><p>ຕົວຢ່າງການໃຊ້ງານ: ໃນພາສາອັງກິດສຳລັບຊ່ວງຄ່າ "
"(1878&#x2013;1903), ສຳລັບຄວາມສຳພັນ/ການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ (Zurich&#x2013;Dublin). "
"ໃນພາສາເຢຍລະມັນຍັງໃຊ້ (ມີຍະຫວ່າງ!) ສຳລັບການສະແດງຄວາມຄິດ: &ldquo;Es war &#x2013; wie "
"immer in den Ferien &#x2013; ein regnerischer Tag.</p> <p>ເບິ່ງ <a href="
"\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dash\">Wikipedia:Dash</a></p>"

#: src/titler/unicodedialog.cpp:186
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>An em Dash (dash of the width of an m).</p><p>Usage examples: In English "
"language to mark&#x2014;like here&#x2014;thoughts. Traditionally without "
"spaces. </p><p>See <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dash\">Wikipedia:"
"Dash</a></p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Em Dash (ຂີດທີ່ມີຄວາມກວ້າງຂອງ m).</p><p>ຕົວຢ່າງການໃຊ້ງານ: ໃນພາສາອັງກິດເພື່ອໝາຍ&#x2014;"
"ຄືກັບບ່ອນນີ້&#x2014;ຄວາມຄິດ. ຕາມປະເພນີແມ່ນບໍ່ມີຍະຫວ່າງ. </p><p>ເບິ່ງ <a href=\"https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/Dash\">Wikipedia:Dash</a></p>"

#: src/titler/unicodedialog.cpp:189
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>Narrow no-break space. Has the same width as U+2009.</p><p>Usage: For "
"units (spaces are marked with U+2423, &#x2423;): 230&#x2423;V, "
"&#x2212;21&#x2423;&deg;C, 50&#x2423;lb, <em>but</em> 90&deg; (no space). In "
"German for abbreviations (like: i.&#x202f;d.&#x202f;R. instead of i.&#xa0;d."
"&#xa0;R. with U+00a0).</p><p>See <a href=\"https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Schmales_Leerzeichen\">Wikipedia:de:Schmales_Leerzeichen</a></p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Narrow no-break space. ມີຄວາມກວ້າງເທົ່າກັບ U+2009.</p><p>ການໃຊ້ງານ: ສຳລັບຫົວໜ່ວຍ "
"(ຍະຫວ່າງຖືກໝາຍດ້ວຍ U+2423, &#x2423;): 230&#x2423;V, &#x2212;21&#x2423;&deg;C, "
"50&#x2423;lb, <em>ແຕ່</em> 90&deg; (ບໍ່ມີຍະຫວ່າງ). ໃນພາສາເຢຍລະມັນສຳລັບຄຳຫຍໍ້ (ເຊັ່ນ: i."
"&#x202f;d.&#x202f;R. ແທນທີ່ຈະເປັນ i.&#xa0;d.&#xa0;R. ດ້ວຍ U+00a0).</p><p>ເບິ່ງ <a "
"href=\"https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Schmales_Leerzeichen\">Wikipedia:de:"
"Schmales_Leerzeichen</a></p>"

