#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (KMessageWidget, info_message)
#: src/ui/clipjobmanager_ui.ui:80
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"In the arguments, the following options are available: <ul><li><b>{source}</"
"b> will be replaced by the Bin Clip source file path</li><li><b>{param1}</b> "
"will be replaced by the first parameter value</li><li><b>{param2}</b> will "
"be replaced by the second parameter value</li><li><b>{output}</b> will be "
"replaced by the output file name</li></ul>"
msgstr ""
"ໃນ arguments, ຕົວເລືອກຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ສາມາດໃຊ້ໄດ້: <ul><li><b>{source}</b> "
"ຈະຖືກແທນທີ່ດ້ວຍເສັ້ນທາງໄຟລ໌ຕົ້ນສະບັບຂອງຄລິບ Bin</li><li><b>{param1}</b> "
"ຈະຖືກແທນທີ່ດ້ວຍຄ່າພາຣາມິເຕີທີໜຶ່ງ</li><li><b>{param2}</b> ຈະຖືກແທນທີ່ດ້ວຍຄ່າພາຣາມິເຕີທີສອງ</"
"li><li><b>{output}</b> ຈະຖືກແທນທີ່ດ້ວຍຊື່ໄຟລ໌ຜົນລັບ</li></ul>"

